'''亞洲青年男子手球錦標賽'''為[[亞洲手球總會|亞洲手球總會]]主辦的兩年一屆亞洲青年男子手球賽事.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asianhandball.org/index.php?option=com_champion&view=lists&champion_type=3&Itemid=292&lang=en|title=Asian Men's Junior Championship History|publisher=[[Asian_Handball_Federation|Asian Handball Federation]]|accessdate=21 October 2015|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821065038/http://www.asianhandball.org/index.php?option=com_champion&view=lists&champion_type=3&Itemid=292&lang=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.handball-planet.com/asian-junior-championship-2014-iran-qatar-going-for-a-hat-trick/|title=Asian Junior Championship 2014 (Iran): Qatar going for a “hat-trick”|work=handball-planet.com|accessdate=29 October 2015|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512055440/http://www.handball-planet.com/asian-junior-championship-2014-iran-qatar-going-for-a-hat-trick/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。本賽事也為世界青年錦標賽的資格賽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/sports/2014-08/03/c_133527419.htm|title=Iran hosts Asian Junior Handball Championship|date=3 August 2014|publisher=[[Xinhua_News_Agency|Xinhua News Agency]]|accessdate=29 October 2015|archive-date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807002603/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/sports/2014-08/03/c_133527419.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。


